title: Vier Minuten/Four Minutes
description: Tough young Jenny (Hannah Herzsprung, in a meteoric debut peformance) is serving time in a women&#039;s prison in Luckau, Germany. She meets her match in the elderly Traude (Monica Bleibtreu), a Prussian woman who has been teaching piano to the inmates since World War II. But Traude&#039;s near-obsessive attachment to Jenny goes far beyond musical professionalism, becoming something much more fervid and intense. Everything hangs in the balance when the dramatic details of both Jenny and Traude&#039;s pasts threaten to be revealed.
